<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bella Estética — Beleza que transforma</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #F9F5F0;
    --rose: #C8826A;
    --rose-light: #EDD5C8;
    --rose-dark: #9A5C47;
    --charcoal: #2C2420;
    --muted: #8A7A74;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    background: rgba(249,245,240,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,130,106,0.15);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--rose); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--rose); color: white;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8rem 4rem 4rem;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  .hero-text { animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease both; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose); border: 1px solid var(--rose-light);
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border-radius: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 420px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--charcoal); color: white;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--rose); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-ghost {
    color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--rose); }
  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  .hero-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(44,36,32,0.12);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: -30px; right: -30px;
    width: 180px; height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--rose-light);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .hero-img-placeholder {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose-light) 0%, var(--cream) 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 4rem; color: var(--rose);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .stats-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1rem;
  }
  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services {
    padding: 6rem 4rem;
    background: white;
  }
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose); margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 300; color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .section-title em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .services-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }
  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(200,130,106,0.15);
    border-color: var(--rose-light);
  }
  .service-icon {
    width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--rose-light);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem; color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .service-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }
  .service-price {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--rose);
    font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  .testimonials { padding: 6rem 4rem; background: var(--charcoal); }
  .testimonials .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
  .testimonials .section-tag { color: var(--rose-light); }
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 2rem;
  }
  .stars { color: var(--rose); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .testimonial-card p { color: rgba(249,245,240,0.8); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; }
  .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .avatar {
    width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--rose); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; color: white;
  }
  .author-name { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--cream); font-weight: 500; }
  .author-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); }

  /* CONTACT */
  .contact {
    padding: 6rem 4rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .contact h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .contact h2 em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .contact > div > p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .contact-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .contact-info a {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--charcoal); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-info a:hover { color: var(--rose); }
  .contact-info span { font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .contact-form { background: white; border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 2.5rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(44,36,32,0.08); }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
    width: 100%; padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #E8E0DA; border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--charcoal); background: var(--cream);
    transition: border-color 0.2s; outline: none;
  }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus { border-color: var(--rose); }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 100px; }
  .form-submit {
    width: 100%; background: var(--rose); color: white;
    border: none; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 2rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--charcoal); color: rgba(249,245,240,0.5);
    text-align: center; padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  footer span { color: var(--rose); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem; text-align: center; }
    .hero p { margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-btns { justify-content: center; }
    .services { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .testimonials { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .contact { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">bella <span>estética</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#servicos">Serviços</a></li>
    <li><a href="#depoimentos">Depoimentos</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contato">Contato</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contato" class="nav-cta">Agendar</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <div class="hero-badge">✦ Clínica de Estética Premium</div>
    <h1>Beleza que <em>transforma</em> e encanta</h1>
    <p>Tratamentos personalizados com tecnologia de ponta para realçar sua beleza natural. Experimente o cuidado que você merece.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#contato" class="btn-primary">Agendar consulta</a>
      <a href="#servicos" class="btn-ghost">Ver serviços →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="hero-card">
      <div class="hero-img-placeholder">✦</div>
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">1.2k+</div><div class="stat-label">Clientes felizes</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">8 anos</div><div class="stat-label">De experiência</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">98%</div><div class="stat-label">Satisfação</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services" id="servicos">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <span class="section-tag">O que oferecemos</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Nossos <em>serviços</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card reveal">
